{"tid":1576723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所羅門群島與台灣斷交，美國會議員呼籲通過台北法案","createTime":"2019-09-17T11:06:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-18T09:56:26.000Z","uid":63669,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3dff3032d1f69485c538ae7ff40425a604f0cdcb","tid":1576723,"uid":63669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:06:52.000Z","msg":"位於南太平洋的所羅門群島星期一(9月16日)決定與台灣斷交，轉而與中國建交，使得台灣目前的邦交國剩下16個。<br />\n<br />\n美國共和黨參議員加德納(Cory Gardner)透過推特表示，所羅門群島決定與台灣斷交是一項令人遺憾的錯誤，所國應該撤銷這項決定。<br />\n<br />\n加德納還指出，中國對台灣的敵對行為勢必將面對自由世界抵禦的決心，他也呼籲參議院立即考慮他所提出的台北法案(Taipei Act)，讓一些降低與台灣關係，並與中國建立關係的國家吃到苦頭。<br />\n<br />\n另一位共和黨參議員魯比奧(Marco Rubio)也透過官方新聞推特指出，所羅門群島成為最新一個屈服於中國壓力，與台灣斷交的國家，美國與國際社會必須反制北京的霸凌與孤立台灣的行為，現在是國會通過跨黨派議員提出的台北法案的時機了。<br />\n<br />\n美國共和黨眾議員約赫(Ted Yoho)也推文表示，對於所羅門群島終止與台灣的長期關係，轉而與中國建交感到遺憾，他說，台灣是所羅門群島值得信賴的伙伴，也是印太地區重要的民主夥伴，此一決定傷害了台灣並鼓勵了中國共產黨。<br />\n<br />\n台北法案的目的是加強台灣在世界各國的地位，並要求美國採取行動與各國交涉，支持台灣的外交承認或加強非官方關係。如果有國家採取不利台灣的行動，法案將授權美國國務院降低與這些國家的外交關係，暫停或改變相關援助，包括軍事、融資等。"},{"pid":"fa03b3e8e27591f53c1080c2f442c786f2a37350","tid":1576723,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:07:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RQ9fj8y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRQ9fj8y.jpg&h=9615793a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8191512263fd0d8c9b29f97a566af1025859cb5a","tid":1576723,"uid":40267,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:08:16.000Z","msg":"澳洲最撚慘<br />\n成個後欄比支共插旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b9b7878e3024906f05d85d2c06a85976718585e","tid":1576723,"uid":50598,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:08:27.000Z","msg":"不如簡單直接搞個制裁支那法案<br />\n唔洗逐個逐個地方黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e79aff9e585a3e33b8671bae8a499bd4ab9b46b","tid":1576723,"uid":28451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:10:04.000Z","msg":"唔係講唔支持，但美國自己都同台灣斷交左咁多年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />....."},{"pid":"43ae94df4552430f1c5f0e794c5781af65211904","tid":1576723,"uid":4917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:10:41.000Z","msg":"美國咪又係同台灣斷左交<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8ebe3b3fd2c16129005305f47e589bda9192b00","tid":1576723,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:13:25.000Z","msg":"咁你美國又唔同台灣建交<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4784d6b511710f4183d5e1ff0186080445e695c7","tid":1576723,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:17:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87e3f7f547948c2e5d55e7c30059c22177501ffb","tid":1576723,"uid":184371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:25:15.000Z","msg":"如果美國肯同台灣建交，應該好多國家跟"},{"pid":"8c54be7f93ff995bbaa5fabf5bee8c78810873d0","tid":1576723,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8191512263fd0d8c9b29f97a566af1025859cb5a","tid":1576723,"uid":40267,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:08:16.000Z","msg":"澳洲最撚慘<br />\n成個後欄比支共插旗<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T11:41:58.000Z","msg":"佢自己地盤都保唔住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5788465591f2bf0d2072fa6c87366a31d8c84c2","tid":1576723,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87e3f7f547948c2e5d55e7c30059c22